                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>Cape Island</placeName>\n                <date>1st July</date>.</p>\n            <p>My dear <addressee>Mr Leeser</addressee></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">I write this to say “how<lb/> do you do,” &amp; “good bye” I was\n                quite<lb/> sorry I did not see you before our<lb/> departure. How did you enjoy<lb/>\n                yourself ? Did you see many friends?<lb/> When you write tell me all about<lb/> your\n                visit (I have forgotten the place<lb/> that you went to was it\n                    <placeName>Baltimore</placeName><lb/> or <placeName>Salem</placeName>) The only\n                news that I can<lb/> write about will concern all of our<lb/> family for I <hi\n                    rend=\"underline\">flatter</hi> myself that<lb/> you would be more interested\n                in<lb/> our affairs that in strangers.<lb/> The weather has been delightful<lb/> so\n                cool we bathe every day<lb/> expect the bathing will be a great<lb/> deal better\n                next week on account<lb/> of the tide being higher (the tide is<lb/> regulated by\n                the moon)</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3pg1j508/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
