                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>Ma &amp; <persName>Selina</persName> send their love to you<lb/> hoping to see you\n                soon.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(7)\">I remain your fond</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(8)\">friend</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(8)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Corinna</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>P. S. Kiss <persName>Dew Drop</persName> for me tell<lb/> her to <hi rend=\"underline\"\n                    >write me</hi> a letter.</p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
